{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"PerformanceNavigation.redirectCount","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation/redirectCount","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigation_timing_API\">Navigation timing API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation\"><code>PerformanceNavigation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>redirectCount</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation/type\"><code>type</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Navigation Timing に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Performance\"><code>Performance</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigationTiming\"><code>PerformanceNavigationTiming</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming\"><code>PerformanceTiming</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/performance_property\"><code>performance_property</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p>このインターフェイスは <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/navigation-timing/#obsolete\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Navigation Timing Level 2 仕様</a>では非推奨です。代わりに <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigationTiming\"><code>PerformanceNavigationTiming</code></a> インターフェイスを使用してください。</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>従来の <code><strong>PerformanceNavigation</strong></code><strong><code>.redirectCount</code></strong> 読み取り専用プロパティは、ページに到達する前に行われた REDIRECT の数を表す <code>unsigned short</code> を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>amount</em> = <em>performanceNavigation</em>.redirectCount;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">ステータス</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/navigation-timing/#dom-performancenavigation-redirectcount\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Navigation Timing<br><small lang=\"ja\">PerformanceNavigation.redirectCount の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"ブラウザの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.PerformanceNavigation.redirectCount","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation/redirectCount/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"あわせて参照","title":"あわせて参照","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>所属する <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation\"><code>PerformanceNavigation</code></a> インターフェイス</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"仕様","id":"仕様"},{"text":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"ブラウザの互換性"},{"text":"あわせて参照","id":"あわせて参照"}],"summary":"従来の PerformanceNavigation.redirectCount 読み取り専用プロパティは、ページに到達する前に行われた REDIRECT の数を表す unsigned short を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"PerformanceNavigation.redirectCount","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"PerformanceNavigation.redirectCount","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/performancenavigation/redirectcount","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/performancenavigation/redir